  SoaN-chhat8 chiong po2-poe3 eng7 chhia chai3 tng2-khi3 soaN-nih8. Hit si5 Pouh chiah hoat-kak. ¡§Kiong-it hiaN hai7 lah, koaN2-kin2 peh khi2-lai5, thau5-a2 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 soaN-chhat8 lai5¡¨. Kiong-it chheng7 peh8 e5 khun3-saN tui3 bin5-chhng5 peh khi2-lai5. Pouh kong2, ¡§Lan2 koaN2-kin2 lai5 khi3, chiong soaN-chhat8 chhiuN2-khi3 e5 mih8 theh8 tng2-lai5¡¨, chiu7 chai3 Kiong-it chau2 chin kin2. Chhin-chhiuN7 hong, Ng3 chhiu7-na5, koe3 soaN-nia2, bo5 ku2 chiu7 chau2 kau3 soaN-chhat8 e5 chhu3. SoaN-chhat8 e5 chhu3-nih8 u7 ui5 chin koan5 e5 chhiuN5-a2, chhiuN5-a2 goa7 ia7 u7 chit8 tiau5 chin toa7 tiau5 e5 chui2-kau. Chiah-e5 soaN-chhat8 chin hoaN-hi2, in-ui7 in kim-am3 e5 kang-chok chin seng5-kong, chiu7 lim-chiu2, tai7-ke khun3 kau3 chin tang7-bin5. 
